<td valign=top rowspan=2>
<b> The burial chamber of Inherkhau </b>
<BR>
<p>

As with the <a href="sennedjem.html">burial chamber of Sennedjem</a>
we have created, from 32 individual photographs, a single
distortion-free mosaic of the burial chamber of Inherkhau.  Shown to
the right is the progression of the North wall (after removing
geometric distortions).  The final reconstruction shown below is at
1/16 resolution.

<BR><BR>

<a href=inherkhau/virtualtomb/jME_inherkhau.jnlp>Virtual Tomb</a> (use
arrow keys to move, shift-arrow to change view direction, ESC to quit)
